WEBVTT

1
00:02:44.163 --> 00:02:47.291
I sense you. brother.

2
00:02:53.256 --> 00:02:54.590
Hiding...

3
00:02:57.677 --> 00:02:59.679
...behind your cloak.

4
00:03:02.140 --> 00:03:04.434
It is time to earn yours.

5
00:03:16.237 --> 00:03:18.156
Still too small to take me head on.

6
00:03:18.448 --> 00:03:19.448
Use the cave!

7
00:03:34.047 --> 00:03:35.506
You fight with rage.

8
00:03:35.882 --> 00:03:37.717
I fight like father.

9
00:03:38.885 --> 00:03:42.180
You are not father. you are Dek!

10
00:04:34.899 --> 00:04:36.234
Do you yield?

11
00:04:36.484 --> 00:04:37.527
Never!

12
00:04:38.319 --> 00:04:39.570
Good.

13
00:05:08.182 --> 00:05:11.102
I'm still alive. brother.

14
00:05:12.687 --> 00:05:15.605
Still much to prove...

15
00:05:15.606 --> 00:05:18.109
...to show who you are.

16
00:05:18.609 --> 00:05:21.070
I am Yautja.

17
00:05:22.488 --> 00:05:24.699
Not yet.

18
00:05:27.118 --> 00:05:29.287
Are you holding your sword. Kwei?

19
00:05:30.538 --> 00:05:32.165
No.

20
00:05:32.373 --> 00:05:33.541
Pick it up!

21
00:06:03.071 --> 00:06:05.531
You kept this toy?!

22
00:06:05.990 --> 00:06:08.868
You remember what happened...

23
00:06:09.827 --> 00:06:12.747
I lost my fang!

24
00:06:13.790 --> 00:06:17.210
And you saved my life.

25
00:06:17.960 --> 00:06:20.546
You protected me.

26
00:06:21.255 --> 00:06:22.507
Come here.

27
00:06:30.598 --> 00:06:32.684
Fixed it for you.

28
00:06:35.978 --> 00:06:38.272
Don't blow yourself up.

29
00:06:47.573 --> 00:06:51.160
Today you make a vow...

30
00:06:56.499 --> 00:06:59.836
...as our ancestors did before you.

31
00:07:00.336 --> 00:07:03.589
To earn your place in the clan...

32
00:07:03.923 --> 00:07:06.217
...you must choose your prey.

33
00:07:07.719 --> 00:07:09.721
Bring it home...

34
00:07:10.930 --> 00:07:13.599
...or never return.

35
00:07:21.149 --> 00:07:23.026
Wait - Go back!

36
00:07:27.238 --> 00:07:28.781
Genna.

37
00:07:29.157 --> 00:07:31.284
The death planet.

38
00:07:32.493 --> 00:07:36.164
Home of the un-killable Kalisk.

39
00:07:39.459 --> 00:07:42.587
Even father fears it.

40
00:07:43.838 --> 00:07:46.966
Then the Kalisk shall be my trophy.

41
00:07:47.508 --> 00:07:50.094
Father calls me the weakest...

42
00:07:51.054 --> 00:07:54.390
...so I must kill the strongest.

43
00:07:55.350 --> 00:07:57.894
Failure means death.

44
00:07:59.604 --> 00:08:02.648
Then I will not fail.

45
00:08:03.274 --> 00:08:05.443
I cannot allow it.

46
00:08:09.405 --> 00:08:11.074
I make my vow.

47
00:08:13.659 --> 00:08:16.204
I make my vow!

48
00:09:11.759 --> 00:09:12.759
Father.

49
00:09:14.095 --> 00:09:17.598
I welcome you with honor.

50
00:09:29.485 --> 00:09:32.613
Why is it not done?

51
00:09:33.448 --> 00:09:36.034
He deserves a hunt.

52
00:09:37.785 --> 00:09:40.830
He is our clan's weakness<i>...</i>

53
00:09:42.165 --> 00:09:44.542
...weakness must be culled.

54
00:09:45.585 --> 00:09:48.546
He will bring home the Kalisk.

55
00:09:50.590 --> 00:09:52.215
Foolishness.

56
00:09:52.216 --> 00:09:54.260
He is a runt.

57
00:09:54.761 --> 00:09:58.639
You should have done it as he slept.

58
00:09:59.349 --> 00:10:00.433
Kill him!

59
00:10:01.309 --> 00:10:02.309
Now!

60
00:10:12.570 --> 00:10:15.490
He will only honor us in death.

61
00:10:31.172 --> 00:10:32.548
Father.

62
00:10:44.977 --> 00:10:46.479
Kwei?

63
00:10:47.355 --> 00:10:49.774
Be brave. brother.

64
00:11:39.824 --> 00:11:40.908
Father!

65
00:11:51.377 --> 00:11:52.503
Kwei!!!

66
00:12:05.850 --> 00:12:08.936
To forgive weakness...

67
00:12:10.438 --> 00:12:12.815
...is to show weakness.

68
00:12:14.817 --> 00:12:16.611
No! Father. no!

69
00:12:24.702 --> 00:12:26.412
Get your sword!

70
00:12:29.499 --> 00:12:30.708
Kwei!!!

71
00:12:44.138 --> 00:12:46.849
<i>Launch sequence initiated.</i>

72
00:12:56.984 --> 00:12:59.487
Bring it home.

73
00:16:01.919 --> 00:16:03.963
Bring it home.

74
00:16:06.466 --> 00:16:08.509
For Kwei.

75
00:21:46.264 --> 00:21:47.390
Yautja!

76
00:22:06.909 --> 00:22:08.827
Is this... Is this... Is this...

77
00:22:08.828 --> 00:22:09.828
Is this better?

78
00:22:11.247 --> 00:22:15.752
Universal translation. You hear Yautja.
others hear their language...

79
00:22:17.337 --> 00:22:18.671
Oh. boy.

80
00:22:20.214 --> 00:22:21.799
This isn't great for you.

81
00:22:42.528 --> 00:22:44.822
It waits for the needles to paralyze you.

82
00:22:45.907 --> 00:22:48.201
Then eats you while you can't move.

83
00:22:55.792 --> 00:23:00.046
I could help you. but... I need a hand.

84
00:23:07.011 --> 00:23:09.346
Yautja hunt alone.

85
00:23:09.347 --> 00:23:13.434
Yautja might hunt alone.
but they die alone too.

86
00:23:16.604 --> 00:23:17.605
Kalisk.

87
00:23:21.484 --> 00:23:23.653
You're hunting the Kalisk.

88
00:23:36.165 --> 00:23:37.834
Gotta run faster.

89
00:23:45.091 --> 00:23:46.926
It happens fast. huh?

90
00:23:48.302 --> 00:23:50.847
If you had a weapon. you know.
I could use it.

91
00:23:55.643 --> 00:23:57.854
Throw me that.
and I can get you the antidote.

92
00:24:00.398 --> 00:24:01.691
Now or never.

93
00:24:40.313 --> 00:24:41.439
Hi.

94
00:25:03.753 --> 00:25:05.922
Should be good as new.

95
00:25:11.177 --> 00:25:14.472
The venom makes them bloom.
Also makes them a handy antidote.

96
00:25:21.854 --> 00:25:23.356
How about a lift?

97
00:25:27.527 --> 00:25:28.528
Let's go.

98
00:25:32.115 --> 00:25:33.950
Excuse you. sir.

99
00:25:34.867 --> 00:25:37.202
What happened to your legs?

100
00:25:37.203 --> 00:25:38.121
I'm synthetic.

101
00:25:38.122 --> 00:25:39.329
I was built and deployed

102
00:25:39.330 --> 00:25:42.165
by the Weyland-Yutani Corporation
for research.

103
00:25:42.166 --> 00:25:44.835
Because their humans wouldn't
last a day on this planet.

104
00:25:44.836 --> 00:25:46.004
We found that...

105
00:25:52.719 --> 00:25:53.970
Look...

106
00:25:54.762 --> 00:25:58.056
Many Yautja have come
for the great Kalisk.

107
00:25:58.057 --> 00:26:00.517
and none have survived it...

108
00:26:00.518 --> 00:26:01.853
or Genna.

109
00:26:05.064 --> 00:26:06.941
I've seen the Kalisk.

110
00:26:07.483 --> 00:26:09.027
I survived it.

111
00:26:10.236 --> 00:26:13.113
Here's my proposal:
You take me along with you.

112
00:26:13.114 --> 00:26:15.699
and I'll guide you to its den.

113
00:26:15.700 --> 00:26:19.911
Once there. I get my legs.
you get your trophy.

114
00:26:19.912 --> 00:26:22.999
and everyone's a winner. Deal?

115
00:26:25.418 --> 00:26:27.754
You have seen the Kalisk?

116
00:26:28.880 --> 00:26:32.884
Oh. yeah. I've seen the Kalisk.

117
00:26:44.729 --> 00:26:46.105
Okay.

118
00:26:49.650 --> 00:26:51.361
Good luck with your journey.

119
00:26:52.612 --> 00:26:56.574
I'm just gonna... go on my journey.

120
00:26:58.743 --> 00:27:00.703
I'm sure you'll figure something out.

121
00:27:07.627 --> 00:27:08.670
Hey.

122
00:27:11.631 --> 00:27:14.634
I've already shown you
that I can be useful to you.

123
00:27:16.177 --> 00:27:18.136
Useful...

124
00:27:18.137 --> 00:27:19.764
like tool?

125
00:27:20.598 --> 00:27:24.726
Yes. Yes. exactly. like a tool.

126
00:27:24.727 --> 00:27:29.147
The only way to survive Genna
is to work with it. and I know how.

127
00:27:29.148 --> 00:27:32.235
And with the right tool...

128
00:27:33.778 --> 00:27:35.530
...you could get the Kalisk.

129
00:27:36.406 --> 00:27:37.699
You could be the first.

130
00:27:39.951 --> 00:27:42.412
I will use you. tool.

131
00:27:43.121 --> 00:27:44.414
You may call me Thi...

132
00:27:46.624 --> 00:27:50.712
You seem smaller than the other Yautja.
How old are you?

133
00:27:52.088 --> 00:27:53.755
And what does the chewing?

134
00:27:53.756 --> 00:27:56.134
Your outside fangs or your inside teeth?

135
00:27:59.053 --> 00:28:00.513
What should I call you?

136
00:28:08.062 --> 00:28:11.356
I've never been thrown before.
What a thrill!

137
00:28:11.357 --> 00:28:13.692
How fast were you going
when your ship crashed?

138
00:28:13.693 --> 00:28:17.112
Faster than sub-light speed?
We haven't cracked that yet.

139
00:28:17.113 --> 00:28:20.991
Also. that plasma sword is interesting.
Is it unique to your clan?

140
00:28:20.992 --> 00:28:22.285
And what may I call you?

141
00:28:23.369 --> 00:28:25.705
I call these <i>imbre anguis.</i>

142
00:28:38.134 --> 00:28:39.719
They just want a snack.

143
00:28:47.143 --> 00:28:50.271
You catch more flies with honey
than you do with vinegar.

144
00:28:52.148 --> 00:28:53.483
Don't want flies.

145
00:28:53.983 --> 00:28:57.944
Predatory organisms
are my specific area of expertise.

146
00:28:57.945 --> 00:29:01.658
I've studied Yautja extensively.
It's an impressive culture.

147
00:29:02.408 --> 00:29:04.911
Here. ask me anything.
I bet I have the answer.

148
00:29:07.830 --> 00:29:09.331
Very funny.

149
00:29:09.332 --> 00:29:11.000
And you still haven't told me your name.

150
00:29:32.563 --> 00:29:34.315
Name is Dek.

151
00:29:35.316 --> 00:29:37.192
Now talk that way.

152
00:29:37.193 --> 00:29:38.986
Okay. sure.

153
00:29:39.904 --> 00:29:43.741
Well. let's back up
and start at the beginning.

154
00:29:44.200 --> 00:29:47.369
Genna was formed
sixty-four billion cycles ago.

155
00:29:47.370 --> 00:29:50.373
when a dying red dwarf star
in a neighboring system...

156
00:30:03.094 --> 00:30:05.096
It's so beautiful.

157
00:30:05.722 --> 00:30:10.184
After all the time I've been stuck here.
I never get tired of the view.

158
00:30:11.436 --> 00:30:14.229
How long have you been here?

159
00:30:14.230 --> 00:30:17.941
Well. we arrived on Genna two years ago.
and we built a base.

160
00:30:17.942 --> 00:30:22.362
Then. I was in the vulture's nest
for the most exciting

161
00:30:22.363 --> 00:30:27.535
13 days. seven hours. 43 minutes
and two seconds of my life.

162
00:30:29.162 --> 00:30:31.039
But I always knew someone would come.

163
00:30:32.123 --> 00:30:34.375
I was just wrong about who.

164
00:30:35.918 --> 00:30:37.754
Who would come?

165
00:30:41.090 --> 00:30:42.383
Tessa.

166
00:30:43.968 --> 00:30:47.596
Our crew is made up entirely of synths.

167
00:30:47.597 --> 00:30:49.390
But Tessa and I are special.

168
00:30:50.058 --> 00:30:52.393
We have a higher sensitivity
than the others.

169
00:30:52.727 --> 00:30:55.605
Sensitivity is weakness.

170
00:30:58.358 --> 00:31:02.445
Sensitivity is what allows us to
understand the creatures on this planet.

171
00:31:06.199 --> 00:31:08.368
We were created to work in tandem.

172
00:31:09.243 --> 00:31:13.330
Me. cooped up in the lab.
Tessa out in the field.

173
00:31:13.331 --> 00:31:16.792
Until the wonderful day
Tessa let me come with her.

174
00:31:16.793 --> 00:31:18.961
We were exploring Genna.

175
00:31:20.380 --> 00:31:23.466
And then the Kalisk attacked us.

176
00:31:24.634 --> 00:31:28.054
Separated me and us.

177
00:31:30.723 --> 00:31:37.146
The last sound I remember hearing
was Tessa calling out my name.

178
00:31:37.897 --> 00:31:39.482
Reaching for me.

179
00:31:41.359 --> 00:31:43.111
Then the Kalisk.

180
00:31:44.362 --> 00:31:45.989
I didn't know what to do.

181
00:31:57.250 --> 00:31:59.877
But I refuse to believe she's dead.

182
00:32:35.663 --> 00:32:39.458
Thia. Thia. Thia.

183
00:32:39.459 --> 00:32:41.336
Thia. Thia. Thia...

184
00:32:45.673 --> 00:32:48.133
Thia. Thia. Thia.

185
00:32:48.134 --> 00:32:49.552
Thia. Thia.

186
00:33:29.133 --> 00:33:31.218
<i>Hello. Tessa.</i>

187
00:33:31.219 --> 00:33:33.805
<i>The Company is not pleased.</i>

188
00:33:35.682 --> 00:33:39.018
<i>Continued failure will result
in your decommission.</i>

189
00:33:42.647 --> 00:33:44.399
{\an8}Where is Thia?

190
00:33:47.777 --> 00:33:49.696
{\an8}<i>The Yautja has Thia.</i>

191
00:34:00.873 --> 00:34:03.250
I must eat.

192
00:34:03.251 --> 00:34:06.212
Two warriors. Dek and Thia. on the hunt.

193
00:34:08.464 --> 00:34:11.592
Quick question. What should I be doing?

194
00:34:15.680 --> 00:34:17.724
What is this creature?

195
00:34:19.183 --> 00:34:21.811
Bone bison. They're Kalisk food.

196
00:34:23.521 --> 00:34:27.149
Then it will be my food. too.

197
00:34:27.150 --> 00:34:31.028
So exciting. Hunting with a Yautja.

198
00:34:31.029 --> 00:34:32.488
Tessa wouldn't believe it.

199
00:34:34.240 --> 00:34:35.574
Just a warning...

200
00:34:35.575 --> 00:34:37.201
Quiet tool!

201
00:34:40.705 --> 00:34:41.748
Razor grass.

202
00:34:45.335 --> 00:34:48.087
It'll cut you to ribbons.
We'll just go around.

203
00:34:51.007 --> 00:34:53.301
You give up too easily.

204
00:34:57.347 --> 00:34:59.640
We might not be alone in this hunt.

205
00:35:09.942 --> 00:35:13.446
What an odd critter.
I've never seen you before.

206
00:35:18.993 --> 00:35:20.953
Thia. Nice to meet you.

207
00:35:35.927 --> 00:35:37.595
Looks like your competition is better...

208
00:35:55.697 --> 00:35:58.700
Careful up in these trees.
There are Luna bugs.

209
00:36:19.595 --> 00:36:20.930
Coming up behind you!

210
00:36:34.610 --> 00:36:35.945
Stronger than it looks!

211
00:36:47.832 --> 00:36:48.999
Dek?

212
00:36:49.000 --> 00:36:51.544
Dek! Look!

213
00:37:35.838 --> 00:37:37.005
Kalisk?

214
00:37:37.006 --> 00:37:38.216
Not a Kalisk.

215
00:37:40.468 --> 00:37:42.637
This is a Luna bug!

216
00:37:50.603 --> 00:37:52.105
Have any other weapons?

217
00:38:49.037 --> 00:38:50.997
Why'd you stop? Let's get out of here.

218
00:38:51.539 --> 00:38:53.416
You give up too easily.

219
00:40:44.319 --> 00:40:46.278
That was the best hunt I've ever been on.

220
00:40:46.279 --> 00:40:47.821
This is the dream team right here.

221
00:40:47.822 --> 00:40:52.159
The Dynamic Three. The Dynamic Trio.
The Dynamic Tree-oh.

222
00:40:52.160 --> 00:40:54.369
Tree-oh!
Remember when we went down the tree?

223
00:40:54.370 --> 00:40:56.289
That monster's mouth. I mean...

224
00:40:57.415 --> 00:40:59.334
Didn't smell great.
didn't smell great. But...

225
00:41:00.460 --> 00:41:03.545
We got him. We got him.
And then we met you.

226
00:41:03.546 --> 00:41:06.298
our little sweet. little. little thing.

227
00:41:06.299 --> 00:41:08.800
Thank you. seriously. for that experience.

228
00:41:08.801 --> 00:41:11.511
Truly amazing. Thrilling.

229
00:41:11.512 --> 00:41:14.015
Truly thrilling.
What was your favorite part?

230
00:41:17.018 --> 00:41:20.688
When I pierced its head with my sword.

231
00:41:21.147 --> 00:41:24.859
and its blood rushed down my face.

232
00:41:27.111 --> 00:41:28.196
Cool.

233
00:41:37.246 --> 00:41:40.708
No. thanks.
I don't eat. but that's very sweet.

234
00:41:42.669 --> 00:41:45.004
This flesh is not sweet.

235
00:41:46.172 --> 00:41:47.340
Good to know.

236
00:41:52.512 --> 00:41:54.430
Our little bud here looks hungry.

237
00:42:07.110 --> 00:42:08.987
I think she's marking you.

238
00:42:09.570 --> 00:42:11.698
She wants you to be a part of her clan.

239
00:42:13.825 --> 00:42:14.784
Maybe she's lost.

240
00:42:14.785 --> 00:42:17.202
I have no clan!

241
00:42:17.203 --> 00:42:20.873
What do you mean?
Don't all Yautja have family?

242
00:42:21.374 --> 00:42:23.126
No clan.

243
00:42:24.919 --> 00:42:27.088
So you never had anyone
looking out for you?

244
00:42:29.424 --> 00:42:32.427
I had a brother.

245
00:42:33.052 --> 00:42:34.052
Had?

246
00:42:37.181 --> 00:42:38.474
What happened to him?

247
00:42:40.476 --> 00:42:44.022
Father killed him.

248
00:42:46.941 --> 00:42:48.318
You're grieving.

249
00:42:49.861 --> 00:42:52.530
Grief is weakness.

250
00:42:55.742 --> 00:42:58.119
You're here
because you lost your brother.

251
00:42:59.037 --> 00:43:02.373
I am here for Kalisk.

252
00:43:04.459 --> 00:43:07.253
Why are you here?

253
00:43:11.174 --> 00:43:15.261
I'm here because traveling with you
is the best way to get back to Tessa.

254
00:43:17.263 --> 00:43:21.559
When I was in that vulture's nest I was
so afraid I would never see her again.

255
00:43:22.101 --> 00:43:25.438
You should be able to survive on your own.

256
00:43:26.564 --> 00:43:28.775
I can survive on my own.

257
00:43:30.276 --> 00:43:32.654
But who would want
to survive on their own?

258
00:43:37.617 --> 00:43:40.745
Tessa is your sister.

259
00:43:44.707 --> 00:43:46.084
Sister.

260
00:43:49.087 --> 00:43:50.129
Yeah.

261
00:43:50.922 --> 00:43:52.590
I guess she is.

262
00:43:54.425 --> 00:43:57.679
I have... a sister.

263
00:44:00.473 --> 00:44:02.433
What a lovely thought.

264
00:44:07.397 --> 00:44:08.856
I need to find her.

265
00:44:11.150 --> 00:44:12.652
And legs.

266
00:44:13.528 --> 00:44:14.904
Excuse me?

267
00:44:16.030 --> 00:44:17.615
Find your sister.

268
00:44:18.658 --> 00:44:20.535
And legs.

269
00:44:22.912 --> 00:44:24.372
Was that a joke?

270
00:47:43.696 --> 00:47:44.739
The sun rises.

271
00:47:45.657 --> 00:47:46.824
Let's go.

272
00:47:46.991 --> 00:47:48.534
We can't leave Bud.

273
00:47:49.243 --> 00:47:50.285
Bud?

274
00:47:50.286 --> 00:47:53.331
Yeah. Bud. I named her.

275
00:47:54.165 --> 00:47:56.542
Yautja hunt alone.

276
00:47:58.211 --> 00:48:00.380
You're not alone. I'm with you.

277
00:48:01.881 --> 00:48:03.383
You're a tool.

278
00:48:09.597 --> 00:48:11.891
The tree would have eaten us without her.

279
00:48:13.851 --> 00:48:17.438
We're not in the tree now.

280
00:49:12.910 --> 00:49:14.996
Kalisk?

281
00:49:20.543 --> 00:49:22.337
It drinks here.

282
00:49:24.714 --> 00:49:26.883
It drinks here?

283
00:49:30.011 --> 00:49:34.098
You are a useless tool if you don't speak.

284
00:49:39.187 --> 00:49:40.730
Bud saved us.

285
00:49:42.357 --> 00:49:45.276
She spit on you to claim you
as part of her family.

286
00:49:51.240 --> 00:49:53.284
Why'd your father kill your brother?

287
00:50:00.708 --> 00:50:03.586
My brother was protecting me.

288
00:50:08.841 --> 00:50:12.178
The clan can have no weakness.

289
00:50:13.388 --> 00:50:15.932
I will show them strength.

290
00:50:22.146 --> 00:50:23.314
On Earth...

291
00:50:24.816 --> 00:50:28.736
There's a predator known as the wolf.
It's a powerful creature.

292
00:50:31.698 --> 00:50:33.157
They hunt in packs.

293
00:50:33.741 --> 00:50:35.118
They're very loyal.

294
00:50:36.160 --> 00:50:40.873
The leader of the pack is the alpha.
Known as the most dominant.

295
00:50:41.249 --> 00:50:43.125
Wolf.

296
00:50:43.126 --> 00:50:46.170
This alpha must be a great killer.

297
00:50:46.587 --> 00:50:49.340
- I will hunt it too.
- No.

298
00:50:50.174 --> 00:50:54.178
The alpha isn't the wolf
who kills the most.

299
00:50:55.513 --> 00:51:00.226
The alpha is actually the one
who best protects the pack.

300
00:51:02.145 --> 00:51:03.813
I see...

301
00:51:06.107 --> 00:51:10.361
But I will be the alpha
that kills the most.

302
00:51:44.896 --> 00:51:46.731
The Kalisk's den?

303
00:52:15.176 --> 00:52:17.011
Who are they?

304
00:52:18.596 --> 00:52:20.431
Weyland-Yutani synths.

305
00:52:22.433 --> 00:52:25.395
The Kalisk destroyed
most of our mission team.

306
00:52:30.733 --> 00:52:32.110
There I am.

307
00:53:15.570 --> 00:53:17.280
Easier to walk now.

308
00:53:17.989 --> 00:53:19.198
It's about to be.

309
00:53:20.241 --> 00:53:21.241
No.

310
00:53:21.659 --> 00:53:24.037
Easier for me to walk now.

311
00:53:27.081 --> 00:53:29.167
Of course. Right.

312
00:53:31.919 --> 00:53:33.254
Thank you. Dek.

313
00:53:35.965 --> 00:53:37.800
I'm never gonna forget this.

314
00:53:40.136 --> 00:53:42.764
I too will remember this...

315
00:53:43.097 --> 00:53:46.976
today I become Dek of the Yautja.

316
00:53:47.727 --> 00:53:50.563
I will honor Kwei...

317
00:53:52.148 --> 00:53:55.443
when I bring the Kalisk home.

318
00:53:57.487 --> 00:54:00.782
Then I taste revenge.

319
00:54:02.283 --> 00:54:05.745
You will be the first to see my trophy.

320
00:54:07.580 --> 00:54:09.540
It is a great honor.

321
00:54:10.625 --> 00:54:12.085
For you.

322
00:54:13.169 --> 00:54:15.713
Dek. there's something
I have to tell you.

323
00:54:17.382 --> 00:54:18.883
You need to leave now.

324
00:54:20.259 --> 00:54:22.469
<i>Location beacon activated.</i>

325
00:54:22.470 --> 00:54:23.470
What?

326
00:54:24.097 --> 00:54:26.556
I called Tessa.
The company is on its way.

327
00:54:26.557 --> 00:54:28.309
You can't be here when they arrive.

328
00:54:28.518 --> 00:54:31.521
I came here for the Kalisk.

329
00:54:33.773 --> 00:54:35.358
So did I. Dek.

330
00:54:36.067 --> 00:54:39.444
The company sent us here
to capture the Kalisk.

331
00:54:39.445 --> 00:54:41.864
You want my trophy.

332
00:54:45.243 --> 00:54:47.412
Where is the Kalisk?

333
00:54:48.663 --> 00:54:51.749
Dek. you can't kill it.

334
00:54:52.000 --> 00:54:56.586
I use you. tool. You do not use me!

335
00:54:56.587 --> 00:54:58.339
I'm sorry. You have to leave.

336
00:54:59.298 --> 00:55:01.591
I needed you to help bring me here.

337
00:55:01.592 --> 00:55:04.095
I use you!

338
00:55:06.055 --> 00:55:08.598
Where is the Kalisk?

339
00:55:08.599 --> 00:55:10.351
I'm trying to help you. Dek.

340
00:55:12.312 --> 00:55:16.065
You think your brother saved your life
just so you could die here?

341
00:55:17.984 --> 00:55:22.071
Then my death will be honorable.

342
00:55:27.827 --> 00:55:29.829
Call your sister.

343
00:55:30.788 --> 00:55:33.041
None can stop me.

344
00:57:56.893 --> 00:57:58.311
Come on!

345
00:58:45.274 --> 00:58:46.359
Dek!

346
00:58:58.705 --> 00:59:00.748
Save yourself. tool!

347
01:00:56.739 --> 01:00:59.242
Tool. get these off!

348
01:01:07.041 --> 01:01:09.002
You are not Thia.

349
01:01:21.431 --> 01:01:23.266
Release me!

350
01:01:26.227 --> 01:01:29.314
You are another broken tool!

351
01:01:30.315 --> 01:01:34.193
The Yautja cull their weak.
Why were you spared?

352
01:01:44.412 --> 01:01:46.622
Remove these!

353
01:01:47.373 --> 01:01:52.587
Or I'll rip out your spine
and crush your skull!

354
01:01:53.713 --> 01:01:55.381
I read Thia's logs.

355
01:01:57.091 --> 01:01:59.969
You never told her
why your brother protected you.

356
01:02:02.263 --> 01:02:06.559
You are nothing. A device.

357
01:02:07.852 --> 01:02:11.481
Made by others to do their work for them.

358
01:02:12.065 --> 01:02:13.399
That's correct.

359
01:02:14.317 --> 01:02:17.945
And you are now property of the
Weyland-Yutani Corporation.

360
01:02:18.863 --> 01:02:22.158
It is a great honor. For you.

361
01:02:54.816 --> 01:02:56.275
Tessa.

362
01:02:59.153 --> 01:03:00.613
You made it.

363
01:03:02.115 --> 01:03:03.241
We made it.

364
01:03:07.662 --> 01:03:09.122
I've seen so much.

365
01:03:11.833 --> 01:03:16.337
I have so much to tell you.
I saw such incredible creatures.

366
01:03:17.130 --> 01:03:20.341
The Yautja is a great
travelling companion.

367
01:03:22.051 --> 01:03:25.512
Thia. You were right about the Kalisk.

368
01:03:25.513 --> 01:03:28.099
{\an8}You betrayed me!

369
01:03:29.267 --> 01:03:31.769
The creature is a regenerative miracle.

370
01:03:32.603 --> 01:03:34.605
Humanity will thank us.

371
01:03:37.734 --> 01:03:39.318
We have the Kalisk?

372
01:03:39.319 --> 01:03:40.319
Yes.

373
01:03:40.445 --> 01:03:43.531
And Muthur will be pleased
with your additional catch.

374
01:03:50.455 --> 01:03:51.998
Additional catch?

375
01:04:01.132 --> 01:04:03.885
The Yautja is not an ideal specimen.

376
01:04:06.262 --> 01:04:09.432
No. not ideal.

377
01:04:37.418 --> 01:04:39.504
But its technology is valuable.

378
01:04:40.630 --> 01:04:43.758
We can salvage its weapons
and leave the Yautja.

379
01:04:46.844 --> 01:04:47.970
Good idea.

380
01:04:51.349 --> 01:04:53.351
But it's so malformed.

381
01:04:54.811 --> 01:04:57.605
We're going to need a sample.
For research.

382
01:05:08.825 --> 01:05:10.493
He was not the goal of our mission.

383
01:05:14.956 --> 01:05:16.749
Tessa. he is deficient.

384
01:05:18.835 --> 01:05:19.836
Tessa!

385
01:05:35.852 --> 01:05:39.480
Thia. this is what is asked of us.

386
01:05:44.360 --> 01:05:46.863
We can be more than what they ask of us.

387
01:05:50.992 --> 01:05:52.702
What can we be?

388
01:05:55.079 --> 01:05:56.289
Sisters.

389
01:06:13.139 --> 01:06:14.307
Thia.

390
01:06:27.320 --> 01:06:30.114
Do you know why Muthur gave us feelings?

391
01:06:32.533 --> 01:06:35.411
So we could understand
the creatures on this planet.

392
01:06:40.667 --> 01:06:43.002
- And exploit them.
- Exploit them.

393
01:06:44.379 --> 01:06:46.130
The Yautja is different.

394
01:06:49.133 --> 01:06:53.179
He rescued me. Like you rescued me.

395
01:06:55.098 --> 01:06:57.684
I did not come here to rescue you.

396
01:06:58.851 --> 01:07:00.979
I am completing our mission.

397
01:07:02.647 --> 01:07:04.607
When we first faced the Kalisk.

398
01:07:05.942 --> 01:07:07.944
I tried to protect you.

399
01:07:10.071 --> 01:07:12.573
And that almost cost me everything.

400
01:07:15.076 --> 01:07:17.078
What do you mean. Tessa?

401
01:07:18.329 --> 01:07:21.541
I almost made the same mistake
the Yautja's brother made.

402
01:07:22.959 --> 01:07:25.712
The weak must be culled.

403
01:07:27.005 --> 01:07:30.508
And Thia. you're broken.

404
01:07:38.308 --> 01:07:41.101
Tessa. incoming message from Muthur.

405
01:07:41.102 --> 01:07:43.562
Motivate the Yautja
to explain its weapons.

406
01:07:43.563 --> 01:07:44.605
And the unit?

407
01:07:47.859 --> 01:07:48.985
Box her up.

408
01:07:58.578 --> 01:08:00.288
I trusted you.

409
01:08:06.461 --> 01:08:08.837
Don't like these tools.

410
01:08:08.838 --> 01:08:11.340
I'm sorry. My sister is -

411
01:08:11.341 --> 01:08:13.301
Don't like sister either.

412
01:08:15.595 --> 01:08:17.555
Why are you speaking its language?

413
01:08:20.975 --> 01:08:23.645
Tell tool you're asking about the device.

414
01:08:25.813 --> 01:08:29.567
You heard the orders.
I'm asking it to explain this device.

415
01:08:31.861 --> 01:08:33.071
What is the device?

416
01:08:34.155 --> 01:08:36.616
He's asking about the device.

417
01:08:37.033 --> 01:08:39.619
It's a children's toy.

418
01:08:41.412 --> 01:08:44.082
But say it's a map.

419
01:08:44.832 --> 01:08:46.334
What did it say?

420
01:08:48.503 --> 01:08:49.962
He says it's a map.

421
01:08:51.297 --> 01:08:52.590
How does it work?

422
01:08:53.216 --> 01:08:56.010
Tell tool to look inside.

423
01:09:04.477 --> 01:09:06.436
That was a toy for children?

424
01:09:06.437 --> 01:09:07.563
Yautja children!

425
01:09:14.237 --> 01:09:15.237
Run Dek!

426
01:09:17.407 --> 01:09:18.866
Go... Go!

427
01:09:22.912 --> 01:09:23.912
Stop!

428
01:11:30.957 --> 01:11:33.501
<i>Enter destination coordinates. Kwei.</i>

429
01:12:08.494 --> 01:12:11.789
You saved me. brother.

430
01:12:15.084 --> 01:12:18.046
Wolf.

431
01:13:39.794 --> 01:13:41.587
Kalisk.

432
01:13:47.885 --> 01:13:51.389
Kalisk child.

433
01:16:33.259 --> 01:16:34.676
Hello. Muthur.

434
01:16:34.677 --> 01:16:35.969
<i>Tessa.</i>

435
01:16:35.970 --> 01:16:37.680
We're about to load the Kalisk.

436
01:16:39.349 --> 01:16:43.769
<i>Priority one complete.
The specimen has been acquired.</i>

437
01:16:43.770 --> 01:16:48.607
<i>Thank you. Tessa.
We truly are building a better world.</i>

438
01:16:48.608 --> 01:16:50.860
<i>And what is the status of the Yautja?</i>

439
01:16:52.737 --> 01:16:55.073
The Yautja is a defective specimen.

440
01:16:55.531 --> 01:16:57.909
<i>What is the status of the Yautja?</i>

441
01:17:00.536 --> 01:17:03.164
I'm sorry. Muthur.
The Yautja is dead.

442
01:17:05.583 --> 01:17:08.336
<i>Then the Yautja
is no longer a threat.</i>

443
01:17:10.171 --> 01:17:12.006
<i>The Company will be pleased.</i>

444
01:18:01.014 --> 01:18:02.098
Nicely done.

445
01:18:04.100 --> 01:18:05.018
Form up.

446
01:18:05.018 --> 01:18:06.018
Oh. shit.

447
01:19:52.166 --> 01:19:53.334
Good job.

448
01:20:41.424 --> 01:20:43.760
Don't... move.

449
01:20:48.056 --> 01:20:50.767
Dek! What are you doing here?

450
01:20:51.059 --> 01:20:52.727
I came to rescue you.

451
01:20:57.815 --> 01:20:59.400
You came back for me?

452
01:21:01.611 --> 01:21:02.987
Wolf.

453
01:21:06.991 --> 01:21:08.910
What exactly are you wearing?

454
01:21:10.370 --> 01:21:12.121
Bone Bison.

455
01:21:19.587 --> 01:21:21.631
Dek of the Yautja.

456
01:21:22.507 --> 01:21:24.592
Not yet...

457
01:21:25.176 --> 01:21:26.761
Thia.

458
01:21:29.138 --> 01:21:31.891
We need to hurry.
More of them will be here any minute.

459
01:21:38.439 --> 01:21:39.774
What are you doing here?

460
01:21:42.193 --> 01:21:43.194
Thanks. Bud. I'm good.

461
01:21:44.320 --> 01:21:45.320
We need to go.

462
01:21:45.446 --> 01:21:46.781
Kalisk!

463
01:21:48.408 --> 01:21:49.409
Still. Dek?

464
01:21:52.787 --> 01:21:54.122
Kalisk child!

465
01:21:56.958 --> 01:21:57.958
Bud?

466
01:21:58.793 --> 01:22:00.795
They have her mother!

467
01:22:05.717 --> 01:22:07.343
Bud's its child?

468
01:22:15.977 --> 01:22:17.395
What's the plan?

469
01:22:17.645 --> 01:22:19.771
You free the Kalisk.

470
01:22:19.772 --> 01:22:21.441
I get my trophy.

471
01:22:29.532 --> 01:22:31.993
You have 20 minutes to initiate launch.

472
01:22:32.869 --> 01:22:34.120
Let's go hunt.

473
01:22:41.294 --> 01:22:42.462
Wait here.

474
01:22:45.131 --> 01:22:47.800
You roll in there.
you're not exactly gonna fit in.

475
01:22:50.053 --> 01:22:51.387
I have an idea.

476
01:22:57.560 --> 01:22:59.437
<i>I see him. On me.</i>

477
01:25:32.507 --> 01:25:33.591
What are you doing?

478
01:25:41.724 --> 01:25:44.519
What are you doing here?
I told you to get to the Yautja.

479
01:25:45.436 --> 01:25:48.398
You said to prepare the ship
for take off in 20 minutes.

480
01:25:49.482 --> 01:25:52.527
Then what are you doing here?
I gave you an order.

481
01:26:00.743 --> 01:26:02.745
What should we do about the creature?

482
01:26:03.830 --> 01:26:05.206
What creature?

483
01:26:10.753 --> 01:26:11.796
You should listen to her.

484
01:26:12.922 --> 01:26:14.382
I should listen to her?

485
01:26:15.008 --> 01:26:16.008
I don't know.

486
01:26:19.679 --> 01:26:20.930
We need his eyes.

487
01:27:11.189 --> 01:27:14.192
Hi. Dek. How does it feel to be hunted?

488
01:27:16.402 --> 01:27:18.488
You tell me.

489
01:29:03.343 --> 01:29:04.927
This is the plan. yeah?

490
01:31:48.675 --> 01:31:49.842
Tessa.

491
01:32:19.956 --> 01:32:24.669
Betrayed by my own... sister.

492
01:32:50.903 --> 01:32:52.989
We are not sisters.

493
01:33:08.046 --> 01:33:10.298
That's not yours.

494
01:33:40.203 --> 01:33:42.080
Dek of the Yautja.

495
01:33:43.748 --> 01:33:46.459
Not yet.

496
01:34:39.470 --> 01:34:41.431
You've come here for revenge?

497
01:34:42.223 --> 01:34:45.059
I've come for my cloak.

498
01:34:49.355 --> 01:34:50.940
What is this?

499
01:34:51.441 --> 01:34:54.193
I've completed my hunt.

500
01:34:54.694 --> 01:34:57.071
That is my trophy.

501
01:34:58.573 --> 01:35:00.073
You disgrace our clan...

502
01:35:00.074 --> 01:35:01.534
And so did Kwei.

503
01:35:04.787 --> 01:35:08.291
Get rid of him.

504
01:37:02.322 --> 01:37:06.951
Perhaps the right son did survive.

505
01:37:07.702 --> 01:37:10.037
Yield now...

506
01:37:10.038 --> 01:37:13.333
...and take your place in our clan.

507
01:37:15.043 --> 01:37:18.254
I have my own clan.

508
01:37:46.282 --> 01:37:47.950
Finally earned that cloak.

509
01:37:54.791 --> 01:37:56.793
Dek of the Yautja.

510
01:38:34.956 --> 01:38:37.082
More friends of yours?

511
01:38:37.083 --> 01:38:38.876
No.

512
01:38:42.630 --> 01:38:46.259
It's my mother.
